    ('cat_baby_safe_mirror', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for floor face chats', 'Activity Floor Mirror - Pigee Colour Mix', 'Done by Deer', 'Natural Baby Shower', 'https://www.naturalbabyshower.co.uk/products/done-by-deer-activity-floor-mirror-pigee-colour-mix', NULL, 'GBP 34.95', 'in_stock', NULL, 'A sturdy fabric floor mirror with a soft Pigee character border, sized for tummy time on the playmat so your baby can meet a face while you sit beside them.', 'At one to three months, faces still pull the strongest look. A floor mirror gives them something to lock onto during short tummy spells without you leaning over the whole time. You stay close, they practise lifting and looking, and the chat stays shared rather than forced.', 'At one to three months, faces still pull the strongest look. A floor mirror gives them something to lock onto during short tummy spells without you leaning over the whole time. You stay close, they practise lifting and looking, and the chat stays shared rather than forced.', NULL, NULL, true, 'Good gift', NULL, 'Use only during supervised awake play; do not place loose mirrors or toys in the sleep space.', NULL, ARRAY[]::text[], 'none'),
